history.content:
Want to win some money and a free trip to the US Finals? Submit your side project, hackathon project, concept, etc to the Microsoft Imagine Cup!
 
It doesn't have to be a finished product, we accept everything (prototypes, MVPs, etc).
 
Submissions can take as little as 5 minutes!
 
---
 
Details:
 
Top 12 get a free trip, top 9 win cash prizes ranging from $1k-10k.
 
And a side note... there are only a few entries across the US so y'all have a great chance of making it in.
 
Submission guide + UC Berkeley info: https://goo.gl/VbFxGE
 
Feel free to reach out to any Berkeley Microsoft Student Partners for advice: https://facebook.com/MicrosoftBerkeley
history.subject: Submit a side project to the Microsoft Imagine Cup!
